I'm home.

527
00:42:13,619 --> 00:42:17,289
Hey, Pil Sung! You...

528
00:42:17,289 --> 00:42:19,569
Go Pil Sung.

529
00:42:19,569 --> 00:42:23,619
Go Pil Sung, what are you doing right now?

530
00:42:23,619 --> 00:42:28,209
You're holding hands in front of us. Is this a protest?

531
00:42:28,209 --> 00:42:32,699
Miss! Why are you holding my son's hand?

532
00:42:37,839 --> 00:42:41,889
Mom, Dad, Grandma, and Aunt.

533
00:42:41,889 --> 00:42:45,749
I'll be seeing Ji Yeong officially starting today.

534
00:42:45,749 --> 00:42:51,649
So, please treat me as my girlfriend from now on.

535
00:42:51,649 --> 00:42:54,129
What? Girlfriend?

536
00:42:54,129 --> 00:42:56,899
Who said she could be your girlfriend?

537
00:42:57,609 --> 00:43:01,039
Miss, what are you doing right now?

538
00:43:01,039 --> 00:43:04,779
You said nothing is going on between you two. You said not to worry.

539
00:43:04,779 --> 00:43:08,119
How could you stab us in the back like this?

540
00:43:15,279 --> 00:43:17,089
Ma'am,

541
00:43:17,949 --> 00:43:21,309
I'm sorry I couldn't keep the promise.

542
00:43:21,309 --> 00:43:26,209
I tried not to like him, but it didn't work.

543
00:43:26,209 --> 00:43:30,469
I'll be so good to the Director and the rest of the family, too.

544
00:43:30,469 --> 00:43:34,379
I'll do my best to be liked by you.

545
00:43:34,379 --> 00:43:39,539
And I'll work hard to become good enough for Director.

546
00:43:39,539 --> 00:43:43,249
Please... Please give me a chance.

547
00:43:44,599 --> 00:43:46,379
Give you a chance?

548
00:43:46,379 --> 00:43:48,619
What do you mean give you a chance?

549
00:43:48,619 --> 00:43:53,009
You little... You're so shameless, aren't you?

550
00:43:53,009 --> 00:43:55,159
There's no need to talk more.

551
00:43:55,159 --> 00:43:58,329
Miss, please move out immediately.

552
00:43:58,329 --> 00:44:01,609
Move out right now. I don't want to see you.

553
00:44:01,609 --> 00:44:05,529
Mom, you don't have the right to do that.

554
00:44:05,529 --> 00:44:08,939
The room is for the tenant, Ji Yeong, during the contract period.

555
00:44:08,939 --> 00:44:10,379
What?

556
00:44:10,379 --> 00:44:12,949
Ji Yeong, how long is your contract?

557
00:44:12,949 --> 00:44:15,149
Well, two years.

558
00:44:15,149 --> 00:44:18,449
You have the power for two years.

559
00:44:18,449 --> 00:44:23,699
So, you don't have to move out, no matter what my mom says, okay?

560
00:44:24,799 --> 00:44:29,619
Director, why would you say that? You're upsetting her.

561
00:44:29,619 --> 00:44:32,779
Calm down, Director. Don't do it.

562
00:44:32,779 --> 00:44:36,819
Okay. I won't do it since you don't want me to.

563
00:44:43,389 --> 00:44:47,349
Grandmother, Landlady, Ahjussi, and Myeong Dong.

564
00:44:47,349 --> 00:44:50,199
It's getting late. I'll get going now.

565
00:44:50,199 --> 00:44:53,109
Anyway, I hope we get along.

566
00:44:53,109 --> 00:44:54,809
Thank you in advance.

567
00:44:54,809 --> 00:44:56,799
Have a good night, then.

568
00:44:56,799 --> 00:44:59,899
- Let me walk you over. Let's go. 
 - Okay.

569
00:45:00,739 --> 00:45:03,659
- Hey... 
 - Hey, hey!

570
00:45:04,749 --> 00:45:07,939
- Honey. 
 - Unni, are you okay?

571
00:45:09,459 --> 00:45:12,679
- Honey. 
 - Aigoo.

572
00:45:17,679 --> 00:45:23,179
My heart is still pounding, and my legs are shaky, too.

573
00:45:23,179 --> 00:45:26,119
I feel so bad for the landlady.

574
00:45:26,119 --> 00:45:30,499
Looks like everyone is in shock because of me.

575
00:45:30,499 --> 00:45:32,369
What do I do?

576
00:45:32,369 --> 00:45:35,469
It's okay, Ji Yeong.

577
00:45:35,469 --> 00:45:37,119
You did a great job today.

578
00:45:37,119 --> 00:45:39,239
Just keep doing what you did.

579
00:45:39,239 --> 00:45:41,169
Just trust me, okay?

580
00:45:43,659 --> 00:45:45,339
Okay.

581
00:45:45,339 --> 00:45:49,819
I'll only trust you from now on, okay?

582
00:45:51,689 --> 00:45:54,049
What a good girl you are.

583
00:46:27,239 --> 00:46:29,919
Ji Yeong, what's going on?

584
00:46:29,919 --> 00:46:35,679
Something amazing happened. I wanted to tell you about it first.

585
00:46:35,679 --> 00:46:39,979
Since you're my boyfriend now.

586
00:46:39,979 --> 00:46:44,679
Of course. I should hear about it first if something good happened to you.

587
00:46:44,679 --> 00:46:46,099
What is it?

588
00:46:46,099 --> 00:46:49,949
I just heard from CEO Jae Dong.

589
00:46:50,799 --> 00:46:54,309
Don't be shocked and listen.

590
00:46:54,309 --> 00:46:56,239
I...

591
00:46:56,919 --> 00:47:01,129
was cast as the lead actor in the mini-series!

592
00:47:01,129 --> 00:47:03,249
- Really? 
 - Yes!

593
00:47:03,249 --> 00:47:05,999
Congratulations, Ji Yeong!

594
00:47:06,859 --> 00:47:08,799
Are you okay?

595
00:47:10,949 --> 00:47:12,439
My goodness.

596
00:47:12,439 --> 00:47:16,089
Ji Yeong, I need to go to work now. I'll call you when I get off work.

597
00:47:16,089 --> 00:47:19,179
- Let's celebrate this evening, okay? 
 - Okay.

598
00:47:34,449 --> 00:47:39,049
My gosh, what did I see just now?

599
00:47:39,049 --> 00:47:42,289
We have our eyes wide open and

600
00:47:42,289 --> 00:47:45,359
they're flipping out in the front yard like that?

601
00:47:51,389 --> 00:47:54,939
 My brother, Pil Sung. 

602
00:47:54,939 --> 00:47:59,599
 Thank you so much for becoming such a cool adult. 

603
00:47:59,599 --> 00:48:04,679
 I'll be a good younger sister from now on. 

604
00:48:04,679 --> 00:48:10,979
 Starting now, I'll be on your side, no matter what. 

605
00:48:13,399 --> 00:48:18,919
Ji Yeong, I felt disappointed earlier, to be honest.

606
00:48:18,919 --> 00:48:20,819
Pardon?

607
00:48:20,819 --> 00:48:22,109
Why?

608
00:48:22,109 --> 00:48:24,519
How could you forget about me?

609
00:48:24,519 --> 00:48:27,329
Am I that easy to forget?

610
00:48:28,039 --> 00:48:33,009
Well, I'm sorry. I've been kind of out of it these days.

611
00:48:33,939 --> 00:48:39,389
 So, is she saying she forgot about me because she's been busy? 

612
00:48:40,839 --> 00:48:46,009
Ji Yeong, this is our last meal together, right?

613
00:48:46,009 --> 00:48:49,179
You made a decision already, right?

614
00:48:49,179 --> 00:48:51,609
About you becoming my girlfriend.

615
00:48:51,609 --> 00:48:55,839
Well, CEO Gong, I'm very grateful.

616
00:48:55,839 --> 00:49:00,969
You thought so positively of me and forgave me about the jacket.

617
00:49:00,969 --> 00:49:04,069
I'm so grateful for many things.

618
00:49:04,069 --> 00:49:09,659
But I'll have to refuse to become your girlfriend.

619
00:49:09,659 --> 00:49:11,439
I'm sorry.

620
00:49:11,439 --> 00:49:13,299
Why?

621
00:49:13,299 --> 00:49:16,239
Do you mean you don't have any feelings for me?

622
00:49:16,239 --> 00:49:19,699
Why did you say you'd think about it last time?

623
00:49:19,699 --> 00:49:25,689
I was caught off guard because you asked while we were eating

624
00:49:25,689 --> 00:49:30,249
and if I said no when I was supposed to buy you dinner to compensate you for the jacket,

625
00:49:30,249 --> 00:49:33,399
it would've made us feel uncomfortable while eating.

626
00:49:33,399 --> 00:49:35,949
You've got to be kidding me.

627
00:49:35,949 --> 00:49:40,109
After dragging it out and testing the water?

628
00:49:40,109 --> 00:49:42,299
Are you kidding me right now?

629
00:49:42,299 --> 00:49:45,439
And I should be rejecting you.

630
00:49:45,439 --> 00:49:47,849
You think you can reject me?

631
00:49:52,169 --> 00:49:54,049
I'm sorry.

632
00:49:55,389 --> 00:49:58,759
Thank you for everything all this time.

633
00:49:58,759 --> 00:50:01,589
I'll get going now, then.

634
00:50:19,159 --> 00:50:21,689
What's going on right now?

635
00:50:22,741 --> 00:50:27,601
What did she do to me just now?

636
00:50:35,851 --> 00:50:37,911
Yes, come in.

637
00:50:38,961 --> 00:50:42,571
Ms. Hong, Ms. Kim Tae Hee sent flowers.

638
00:50:42,571 --> 00:50:44,981
My gosh, Tae Hee did?

639
00:50:44,981 --> 00:50:47,681
- Yes. I'll put them here. 
 - Okay.

640
00:50:49,711 --> 00:50:51,511
My gosh.

641
00:50:52,351 --> 00:50:54,681
It smells so good.

642
00:50:54,681 --> 00:50:57,761
By the way, what's with the flowers all of a sudden?

643
00:51:01,201 --> 00:51:06,721
Gosh, Tae Hee. I was just about to call after receiving flowers.

644
00:51:06,721 --> 00:51:08,131
What are these for all of a sudden?

645
00:51:08,131 --> 00:51:12,931
I was going to meet Jin Dan today, but he said you were very sick today.

646
00:51:12,931 --> 00:51:14,601
 I wanted you to recover looking at the flowers. 

647
00:51:14,601 --> 00:51:18,071
 Did come back from the hospital with Jin Dan? 

648
00:51:18,071 --> 00:51:20,621
Huh? H-Hospital?

649
00:51:20,621 --> 00:51:23,571
 Gosh, what's she talking about? 

650
00:51:25,831 --> 00:51:28,111
Mother, are you feeling very sick?

651
00:51:28,111 --> 00:51:31,161
No, no. It's just the flu.

652
00:51:31,161 --> 00:51:33,201
Thank you so much, Tae Hee.

653
00:51:33,201 --> 00:51:35,231
I'll be in touch.

654
00:51:37,181 --> 00:51:41,101
Jin Dan, that punk. He lied to Tae Hee that I was sick.

655
00:51:41,101 --> 00:51:42,971
What's going on?

656
00:51:44,351 --> 00:51:48,951
My gosh, maybe he has another woman.

657
00:51:57,641 --> 00:51:59,621
Secretary Jo, it's me.

658
00:52:00,471 --> 00:52:02,101
Kim Ji Yeong?

659
00:52:02,101 --> 00:52:07,321
You mean Jin Dan is seeing someone pathetic like her? 
    

660
00:52:07,321 --> 00:52:12,601
Ms. Hong, I'd get fired if CEO Gong found out I did this.

661
00:52:12,601 --> 00:52:15,031
Don't worry about that, Secretary Jo.

662
00:52:15,031 --> 00:52:17,891
You think I'd put you in that position?

663
00:52:18,691 --> 00:52:20,211
Thank you, Ms. Hong.

664
00:52:20,211 --> 00:52:23,331
Good work, Secretary Jo. You can leave now.

665
00:52:28,151 --> 00:52:30,351
He has a fiancee.

666
00:52:30,351 --> 00:52:33,601
Jin Dan, that punk is out of his mind.

667
00:52:36,991 --> 00:52:39,491
Gosh, why does she live here?

668
00:52:39,491 --> 00:52:41,911
What's going on?

669
00:52:41,911 --> 00:52:45,941
Seon Yeong! Kim Seon Yeong! Come out!

670
00:52:48,451 --> 00:52:50,261
My gosh!

671
00:52:50,261 --> 00:52:52,001
Ae Gyo!

672
00:52:53,221 --> 00:52:57,051
What's going on, Ae Gyo? What's wrong? Why are you so upset?

673
00:52:57,051 --> 00:52:59,601
Seon Yeong, does someone named Kim Ji Yeong live in your house?

674
00:52:59,601 --> 00:53:01,211
Do you know that girl?

675
00:53:01,211 --> 00:53:02,791
Kim Ji Yeong?

676
00:53:02,791 --> 00:53:04,831
You mean our tenant?

677
00:53:04,831 --> 00:53:07,111
Why are you looking for her?

678
00:53:07,111 --> 00:53:08,611
What? Tenant?

679
00:53:08,611 --> 00:53:10,751
You mean for that rental unit?

680
00:53:10,751 --> 00:53:12,611
Y-Yes.

681
00:53:13,171 --> 00:53:15,901
Hey! Kim Ji Yeong! Come out!

682
00:53:15,901 --> 00:53:18,831
Come out, Kim Ji Yeong!

683
00:53:23,541 --> 00:53:27,561
Who are you? I'm Kim Ji Yeong.

684
00:53:28,241 --> 00:53:29,851
Y-You...

685
00:53:35,451 --> 00:53:37,451
My gosh.

686
00:53:37,451 --> 00:53:40,301
I-It's you.

687
00:53:41,001 --> 00:53:43,091
It's you!

688
00:53:43,091 --> 00:53:46,511
Hey! You bitch!

689
00:53:46,511 --> 00:53:48,491
You gold digger! You bitch!

690
00:53:48,491 --> 00:53:51,171
How dare you stick around Jin Dan?

691
00:53:51,171 --> 00:53:54,581
What are you trying to get from him? You beggar!

692
00:53:54,581 --> 00:53:57,251
What are you doing?

693
00:53:57,251 --> 00:53:59,641
Who's your son, anyway?

694
00:53:59,641 --> 00:54:02,261
- Let go of me! 
 - Just talk instead, Ae Gyo. Please!

695
00:54:02,261 --> 00:54:04,301
Don't do this.

696
00:54:05,831 --> 00:54:10,971
You bitch! Jin Dan has a fiancee, too. A fiancee.

697
00:54:10,971 --> 00:54:13,761
How dare you try to seduce him?

698
00:54:13,761 --> 00:54:17,331
Why would a young woman like you act like a gold digger?

699
00:54:17,331 --> 00:54:19,111
