700
00:54:19,111 --> 00:54:20,901
Seduce?

701
00:54:20,901 --> 00:54:24,131
I didn't do that!

702
00:54:24,131 --> 00:54:25,941
What are you talking about?

703
00:54:25,941 --> 00:54:28,051
Hey! You want this, right?

704
00:54:28,051 --> 00:54:32,261
You attached yourself to Jin Dan to get money from him, right?

705
00:54:32,261 --> 00:54:34,051
