709
00:54:41,701 --> 00:54:43,401
Ji Yeong!

710
00:54:47,041 --> 00:54:48,721
Ji Yeong.

711
00:54:51,631 --> 00:54:53,551
Ahjumma.

712
00:54:53,551 --> 00:54:55,821
What are you doing right now?

713
00:54:55,821 --> 00:54:59,831
Gosh, Pil Sung. Why are you defending her?

714
00:54:59,831 --> 00:55:05,361
S-She seduced my Jin Dan, who's engaged.

715
00:55:05,361 --> 00:55:08,181
Get out of here if you'll say nonsense like that!

716
00:55:08,181 --> 00:55:09,991
Right now!

717
00:55:09,991 --> 00:55:14,451
Get out, Ae Gyo. Let's talk outside.

718
00:55:19,831 --> 00:55:22,001
Ji Yeong.

719
00:55:22,001 --> 00:55:24,221
Ji Yeong, are you okay?

720
00:55:24,221 --> 00:55:25,931
It's okay.

721
00:55:31,751 --> 00:55:37,781
Ae Gyo, did she really seduce your son? Are you sure?

722
00:55:37,781 --> 00:55:41,891
I'm telling you. Why would I come here otherwise?

723
00:55:41,891 --> 00:55:44,491
By the way, what's wrong with Pil Sung?

724
00:55:44,491 --> 00:55:46,241
Why would he defend that bitch?

725
00:55:46,241 --> 00:55:48,851
Was he seduced by her, too, by chance?

726
00:55:48,851 --> 00:55:51,721
He didn't. Why would you say that?

727
00:55:51,721 --> 00:55:55,241
Hey. Kick her out of your house, okay?

728
00:55:58,061 --> 00:56:00,151
What's she talking about?

729
00:56:00,151 --> 00:56:04,941
What does our tenant have to do with her son?

730
00:56:07,251 --> 00:56:08,941
My gosh.

731
00:56:17,991 --> 00:56:21,451
Ji Yeong, drink some warm water.

732
00:56:30,681 --> 00:56:32,791
Are you feeling better?

733
00:56:37,971 --> 00:56:40,260
What happened, Ji Yeong?

734
00:56:40,951 --> 00:56:43,571
Did you meet CEO Gong by chance?

735
00:56:45,861 --> 00:56:47,821
You know, too.

736
00:56:47,821 --> 00:56:53,311
I promised to buy him five meals instead of compensating him for the jacket.

737
00:56:53,311 --> 00:56:56,201
There was just one meal left.

738
00:56:56,201 --> 00:57:00,221
So, I had the last meal with him today.

739
00:57:00,791 --> 00:57:02,361
Was she...

740
00:57:03,251 --> 00:57:05,371
doing that because you ate with him?

741
00:57:05,371 --> 00:57:07,621
I don't know.

742
00:57:07,621 --> 00:57:11,281
CEO Gong wanted to go out with me, but I said no.

743
00:57:11,281 --> 00:57:15,471
So, I thought I wouldn't have to be involved with CEO Gong anymore.

744
00:57:15,471 --> 00:57:19,591
I had no idea something like this would happen.

745
00:57:20,241 --> 00:57:25,121
Director, nothing happened between him and me.

746
00:57:25,121 --> 00:57:27,381
I swear.

747
00:57:28,931 --> 00:57:30,571
Yes, Ji Yeong.

748
00:57:30,571 --> 00:57:34,561
I believe everything you said.

749
00:57:34,561 --> 00:57:36,411
Don't worry.

750
00:57:48,651 --> 00:57:51,751
My gosh, what's going on?

751
00:57:51,751 --> 00:57:55,511
So, our tenant was seeing Pil Sung

752
00:57:55,511 --> 00:57:58,611
and she was seeing your friend's son, too?

753
00:57:58,611 --> 00:58:01,061
Aigoo, aigoo, aigoo.

754
00:58:01,061 --> 00:58:04,191
I can't talk because I'm so flabbergasted.

755
00:58:04,191 --> 00:58:07,921
It can't be. There must be a misunderstanding.

756
00:58:07,921 --> 00:58:10,071
Ji Yeong wouldn't do something like that.

757
00:58:10,071 --> 00:58:13,761
Come on! You can't tell just based on her looks.

758
00:58:13,761 --> 00:58:18,371
She has an innocent face,

759
00:58:18,371 --> 00:58:23,111
but she seduced a rich man like him. She's a serious gold digger.

760
00:58:23,111 --> 00:58:29,011
Pil Sung lost his mind because a gold digger like her seduced him.

761
00:58:30,581 --> 00:58:35,081
Hey! Pil Sung. You can't date her.

762
00:58:35,081 --> 00:58:41,281
I was going to tolerate it, but that bitch is really bad news.

763
00:58:41,281 --> 00:58:45,151
Grandma, how could you talk like that?

764
00:58:45,151 --> 00:58:48,821
There's nothing going on between her and that woman's son. Nothing happened.

765
00:58:48,821 --> 00:58:51,001
So, please don't get the wrong idea.

766
00:58:51,001 --> 00:58:53,231
What do you mean by "wrong idea"?

767
00:58:53,231 --> 00:58:56,231
You think Ae Gyo did that for no reason?

768
00:58:56,231 --> 00:58:59,891
Gosh, I really don't have good feelings about her.

769
00:59:00,521 --> 00:59:05,021
I won't say much. You'd better break up with her.

770
00:59:05,021 --> 00:59:08,711
Ji Yeong has nothing to do with that man.

771
00:59:08,711 --> 00:59:13,071
They did meet a few times, but they only ate together due to a situation.

772
00:59:13,071 --> 00:59:17,831
So, believe me, and don't get funny ideas.

773
00:59:20,341 --> 00:59:23,391
What do you mean by "a situation"?

774
00:59:23,391 --> 00:59:26,620
Why would she eat with an engaged man?

775
00:59:28,811 --> 00:59:32,641
Why do we keep getting gold diggers in that rental unit?

776
00:59:32,641 --> 00:59:38,391
Seon Yeong, we can't have female tenants there anymore.

777
00:59:48,561 --> 00:59:50,340
CEO Gong.

778
00:59:50,951 --> 00:59:54,721
Why did he ask Ji Yeong to buy him meals when he was engaged?

779
00:59:54,721 --> 00:59:56,371
What?

